<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA28">
<l>aṉṟēnaṅ kaṭkāṇu māḻiyāṟ kāruruva</l>
<l>miṉṟēnāṅ kāṇā tiruppatuvu meṉṟēṉuṅ</l>
<l>kaṭkaṇṇāṟ kāṇāta vavvuruvai neñceṉṉu</l>
<l>muṭkaṇṇāṟ kāṇu muṇarntu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That day our eye saw the cloud colour of the one with the discus.</l>
<l>Although today there is existing without seeing [him], always</l>
<l>that form which is not seen by the physical eye will be perceived [and] seen</l>
<l>by the inner eye that is called the heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
